{"tid":2423882,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"兩未成年者獨自抵英求庇","createTime":"2021-02-26T07:38:02.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-26T09:19:18.000Z","uid":25558,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"f1a62520af508e45c3e921216feafbdf12ce6e8c","tid":2423882,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T07:38:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210226/3AD4XHCFANFFJLKFFBCWPKAOCI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210226%2F3AD4XHCFANFFJLKFFBCWPKAOCI%2F&d=6DLEtCU0DjtZYWozPjwd68ls9Dgy9T8na9BfJ9hiblc%3D&h=17963aa2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210226%2F3AD4XHCFANFFJLKFFBCWPKAOCI%2F&h=6a152b6c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210226/3AD4XHCFANFFJLKFFBCWPKAOCI/</a><br />\n<br />\n兩未成年者獨自抵英求庇<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】隨去年7月國安法在港實施，向英國尋求政治庇護的港人暴增。英國內政部更新去年第四季港人申請庇護的統計，去年10月至12月共有21名港人到英尋求政治庇護，比上一季的41宗下跌近一半，但當中包括兩名「無人陪伴的尋求庇護兒童（UASC）」，即與父母或看護人分開，自行抵英求庇的兒童或年輕人。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：申領BNO者首超特區護照<br />\n<br />\n據英內政部統計，2020年第四季共有21人向英國尋求政治庇護，19人為主要申請者，2人。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/gzwWmH7qJlZD28n8rN7IgUU-qIU=/1279x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/FITOB2YKZ5BVVPHB5NSAI5OXWM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FgzwWmH7qJlZD28n8rN7IgUU-qIU%3D%2F1279x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FFITOB2YKZ5BVVPHB5NSAI5OXWM.jpg&h=35800854&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■2020年共有76名港人到英國尋求政治庇護；圖為英國機場口岸。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n去年76人申請 逾半為青年<br />\n<br />\n去年第四季是由2007年起，首次再出現UASC個案，即與父母或看護人分開，自行抵英求庇的兒童或年輕人。兩宗個案分別為一男一女，均是抵達英國機場口岸後即提出申請。<br />\n<br />\n2020年共有76港人到英國尋求政治庇護，。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"724ae228b3a7513b88a5a8465768aea66a8f9868","tid":2423882,"uid":78243,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T07:39:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e5ba2a313c3e8188f8a73bf98fdfad37ee6ed2b","tid":2423882,"uid":361751,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T07:42:07.000Z","msg":"有冇香港人收留<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nCoco哥呢<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n冇年輕人，你哋咁易去到英國？"},{"pid":"ac3d6a8f7e61645c2528beaa6a646a85b86e68da","tid":2423882,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T07:43:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f732eae6f781205924108d3ca925b3280cb84979","tid":2423882,"uid":220942,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T07:55:17.000Z","msg":"仲去到英國？<br />\n係咪轉n次機？"},{"pid":"9c98a6f36f76b6e3b5775991aeb82bef1046b6d8","tid":2423882,"uid":49329,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T08:13:17.000Z","msg":"希望流亡海外手足一切安好"},{"pid":"fcaf8ba465d38bdd006a744e54f55ee6dcaaa8a0","tid":2423882,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9c98a6f36f76b6e3b5775991aeb82bef1046b6d8","tid":2423882,"uid":49329,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T08:13:17.000Z","msg":"希望流亡海外手足一切安好"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T08:17:28.000Z"